<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:05:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列高等法院断然驳回宣布总理内塔尼亚胡不适合任职的上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-flatly-rejects-appeal-to-declare-pm-netanyahu-unfit-for-office/0000018d-7596-d4f1-a18d-f5f611840000</link><description>法官们表示，请愿者，其中包括前国防部长摩西·亚阿隆、前参谋长丹·哈鲁茨和纳马·拉齐米，没有给总理足够的时间做出回应，并包含了法院已经听取的论点</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 20:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-flatly-rejects-appeal-to-declare-pm-netanyahu-unfit-for-office/0000018d-7596-d4f1-a18d-f5f611840000</guid></item><item><title>“与哈马斯勾结的叛徒”：内塔尼亚胡支持针对对手的恶意指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-04/ty-article/.highlight/traitors-in-cahoots-with-hamas-netanyahu-backs-poisonous-claims-against-opponents/0000018d-7515-d971-a38f-75b74dc90000</link><description>自战争开始以来，毒药就在网上传播，阴谋论指责内塔尼亚胡的反对者造成了死亡和破坏。反改革抗议运动的领导人希克马·布雷斯勒 (Shikma Bressler) 并没有平静地对待这些袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 19:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-04/ty-article/.highlight/traitors-in-cahoots-with-hamas-netanyahu-backs-poisonous-claims-against-opponents/0000018d-7515-d971-a38f-75b74dc90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列银行冻结了美国第一轮制裁目标的以色列定居者的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bank-blocks-account-of-israeli-settler-targeted-by-first-round-of-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-7532-d4f1-a18d-f5724bac0000</link><description>以色列国民银行是第一家针对美国总统乔·拜登决定对四名以色列定居者实施制裁而采取行动的以色列银行。预计其他银行也将采取类似措施，以避免在美国产生法律影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 19:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bank-blocks-account-of-israeli-settler-targeted-by-first-round-of-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-7532-d4f1-a18d-f5724bac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁同意延长有争议的公民法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-okays-extension-of-controversial-citizenship-law/0000018d-7541-dd6e-a98d-f563c9fa0000</link><description>该法律最初于 2002 年第二次起义期间通过，该法律禁止巴勒斯坦人与以色列居民结婚而获得以色列居民身份，此后每年都延长该法律</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 18:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-okays-extension-of-controversial-citizenship-law/0000018d-7541-dd6e-a98d-f563c9fa0000</guid></item><item><title>随着哈马斯协议的临近，以色列卫生部修改了照顾被释放人质的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-deal-looms-israels-health-ministry-revises-policy-for-care-of-released-hostages/0000018d-7482-d4f1-a18d-f4f230b90000</link><description>新指令基于 11 月底第一批人质在加沙地带获释后吸取的经验教训</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 17:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-deal-looms-israels-health-ministry-revises-policy-for-care-of-released-hostages/0000018d-7482-d4f1-a18d-f4f230b90000</guid></item><item><title>达西·埃利希 (Dassi Erlich) 打倒了施虐者马尔卡·莱弗 (Malka Leifer)。现在她讲述了她的完整故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dassi-erlich-took-her-abuser-malka-leifer-down-now-she-tells-her-full-story/0000018d-6518-d32e-a3cf-efd8af470000</link><description>达西·埃利希 (Dassi Erlich) 的新回忆录《恶意》(In Bad Faith) 全面展现了现年 36 岁的她作为母亲、姐妹、妻子和女儿、虐待家庭的受害者、操纵性的校长和冷酷的极端正统犹太社区的形象。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dassi-erlich-took-her-abuser-malka-leifer-down-now-she-tells-her-full-story/0000018d-6518-d32e-a3cf-efd8af470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在玩枪时意外杀死朋友后被控鲁莽杀人罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-charged-with-reckless-homicide-after-killing-friend-while-toying-with-gun/0000018d-7486-d971-a38f-75b6da060000</link><description>根据起诉书，23 岁的阿维亚·阿巴约夫 (Aviya Abayof) 来自约旦河西岸定居点 Ma&amp;#39;aleh Adumim，当时他正在玩朋友的枪械，无意中射杀了另一位朋友。在国家安全部长本-格维尔加快授权程序后，枪支拥有者获得了执照</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-charged-with-reckless-homicide-after-killing-friend-while-toying-with-gun/0000018d-7486-d971-a38f-75b6da060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的犹太阿拉伯学校如何应对加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-a-jewish-arab-school-in-israel-copes-with-war-in-gaza/0000018d-7372-d971-a38f-73f29a680000</link><description>犹太人和巴勒斯坦人正在以不同的方式经历着席卷我们的可怕暴力。但在我女儿的学校，一些家庭失去了居住在加沙的亲人，另一些家庭则在 10 月 7 日失去了亲人，每天早上孩子们和老师都会出现，致力于弄清楚如何共同生活</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 15:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-a-jewish-arab-school-in-israel-copes-with-war-in-gaza/0000018d-7372-d971-a38f-73f29a680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府抗议运动领导人希克玛·布雷斯勒回应将她与哈马斯联系起来的阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/israeli-protest-movement-leader-responds-to-conspiratorial-claims-linking-her-to-hamas/0000018d-7489-dd6e-a98d-f4ab7d5c0000</link><description>希克马·布雷斯勒是反对内塔尼亚胡政府司法改革的以色列抗议运动的代表人物之一，他被利库德集团议员指控与哈马斯有联系并参与了 10 月 7 日的袭击，他说，“毒药机器永远不会停止工作”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 15:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/israeli-protest-movement-leader-responds-to-conspiratorial-claims-linking-her-to-hamas/0000018d-7489-dd6e-a98d-f4ab7d5c0000</guid></item><item><title>当麦迪逊广场花园挥舞纳粹党徽旗帜时：“一切都可以归咎于犹太人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-swastika-flags-were-waved-on-madison-square-garden/0000018d-64c4-d915-ad8d-f5fcf4df0000</link><description>一部新纪录片以一个从 1936 年到 1941 年欺骗了 10 万美国人的纳粹组织为主题，该纪录片的创作者将当年的犹太人仇恨与今天的反犹太主义进行了比较</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 14:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-swastika-flags-were-waved-on-madison-square-garden/0000018d-64c4-d915-ad8d-f5fcf4df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技产业乌云密布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dark-clouds-gather-for-israels-tech-industry/0000018d-5fc1-d7f9-a3af-dfe939060000</link><description>加沙战争导致科技行业领导者出现悲观情绪：越来越多的证据表明，以色列科技行业正在落后于世界其他地区，就业预测黯淡、投资下降以及报告大规模招聘的公司数量下降</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 13:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dark-clouds-gather-for-israels-tech-industry/0000018d-5fc1-d7f9-a3af-dfe939060000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列人因涉嫌向耶路撒冷基督教修道院院长吐口水而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-arrested-on-suspicion-of-spitting-on-a-christian-abbot-in-jerusalem/0000018d-73de-d971-a38f-73fef8f50000</link><description>在耶路撒冷老城，犹太人向基督徒礼拜者或附近吐口水的事件已变得普遍，引起了以色列政府官员和宗教领袖的谴责，但一些知名人士认为向基督徒吐口水是“古老的犹太习俗”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 12:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-arrested-on-suspicion-of-spitting-on-a-christian-abbot-in-jerusalem/0000018d-73de-d971-a38f-73fef8f50000</guid></item><item><title>“特拉维夫正在地下室举行派对”：以色列顶级厨师适应新现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-aviv-is-currently-partying-in-basements-top-israeli-chefs-adjust-to-a-new-reality/0000018d-6517-d7f7-adcf-6ddf4f040000</link><description>著名的米其林指南不会来，游客也不会来。哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀之后，以色列美食界如何生存？正如一位成功的厨师所说：“F* 米其林”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 10:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-aviv-is-currently-partying-in-basements-top-israeli-chefs-adjust-to-a-new-reality/0000018d-6517-d7f7-adcf-6ddf4f040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙地带作战行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat-operations/0000018d-7337-dd6e-a98d-f737edd20000</link><description>以色列军方宣布，一名24岁士兵周六在加沙南部被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 09:33:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/idf-reservist-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat-operations/0000018d-7337-dd6e-a98d-f737edd20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在帆板世界锦标赛上获得金牌和铜牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-comes-home-with-gold-and-bronze-medals-at-windsurfing-world-championships/0000018d-732a-dd6e-a98d-f72ae6250000</link><description>在加那利群岛举行的 2024 年帆板世界锦标赛上，两名以色列女子获得奖牌，莎朗·坎特 (Sharon Kantor) 获得金牌，队友凯蒂·斯皮恰科夫 (Katy Spychakov) 获得铜牌。坎特有望代表以色列参加今年夏天的巴黎奥运会</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 09:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-comes-home-with-gold-and-bronze-medals-at-windsurfing-world-championships/0000018d-732a-dd6e-a98d-f72ae6250000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼部长本-格维尔在《华尔街日报》采访中表示，“如果特朗普掌权”，美国对加沙的看法将会有所不同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/far-right-minister-ben-gvir-says-in-wsj-interview/0000018d-72ea-d971-a38f-73fa99c30000</link><description>国家安全部长本-格维尔攻击拜登政府，谈到在经济上激励巴勒斯坦人离开加沙，并重申他反对任何释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的人质协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 07:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/far-right-minister-ben-gvir-says-in-wsj-interview/0000018d-72ea-d971-a38f-73fa99c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队承认未经授权进行图形加沙影响行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-its-admits-staff-was-behind-graphic-gaza-telegram-channel/0000018d-70b4-dd6e-a98d-f4b6a9c00000</link><description>以色列国防军的一个心理战部队在未经批准的情况下开设了一个针对以色列受众的 Telegram 频道。军方最初否认参与其中，但《国土报》曝光后的内部调查显示其参与其中</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 06:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-its-admits-staff-was-behind-graphic-gaza-telegram-channel/0000018d-70b4-dd6e-a98d-f4b6a9c00000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟考虑是否根据美国行政命令对“极端主义”以色列定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/eu-mulls-whether-to-impose-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-settlers/0000018d-71cc-dd6e-a98d-f5eed2050000</link><description>欧盟需要一致投票支持对暴力的约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁，拜登采取行动后这一决定已“加快”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 06:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/eu-mulls-whether-to-impose-sanctions-on-extremist-israeli-settlers/0000018d-71cc-dd6e-a98d-f5eed2050000</guid></item><item><title>拜登向内塔尼亚胡提供生命线，但以色列总理仍拒绝接受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-netanyahu-a-lifeline-but-the-prime-minister-still-refuses-to-take-it/0000018d-70b3-d4f1-a18d-f4f3e2070000</link><description>白宫已开始在中东引入“拜登主义”，尽管内塔尼亚胡仍然使以色列的地位变得脆弱。与此同时，美国一直在小心避免与伊朗发生全面军事对抗</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 05:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/biden-offered-netanyahu-a-lifeline-but-the-prime-minister-still-refuses-to-take-it/0000018d-70b3-d4f1-a18d-f4f3e2070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列等待哈马斯对人质协议的回应；国防部长告诉拜登特使以色列对与黎巴嫩的外交持开放态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-live/u-s-and-allies-strike-over-30-houthi-targets-in-yemen-to-re-stabilize-red-sea/0000018d-7217-d4f1-a18d-f6776d6a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：之前人质协议的比例将作为即将达成的协议的参考点 ■ 民意调查：29％的人支持美国总统乔·拜登对以色列与哈马斯战争的处理方式 ■ 以色列政府批准向加沙扣押的人质支付工资，并追溯支付</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 04:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article-live/u-s-and-allies-strike-over-30-houthi-targets-in-yemen-to-re-stabilize-red-sea/0000018d-7217-d4f1-a18d-f6776d6a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>